and First Schedule (w.e.f. 20-12-1974).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00030_196256_1517807322465&sectionId=32596&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00030_196256_1517807322465)
